query:
INSERT INTO
                protocol_versions (
                    id,
                    bootloader_code_hash,
                    default_account_code_hash,
                    upgrade_tx_hash,
                    executed,
                    created_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, FALSE, NOW())
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
                upgrade_tx_hash = EXCLUDED.upgrade_tx_hash,
                executed = FALSE;
